          <td>Applesauce (¼ cup unsweetened)</td>
          <td class="ratio-cell">¼ cup per egg</td>
          <td class="notes-cell">Adds moisture and mild sweetness. Slightly denser result.</td>
          <td class="best-cell">Cakes, muffins, quick breads</td>
          <td><div class="diet-tags"><span class="diet-tag tag-vegan">V</span><span class="diet-tag tag-ef">EF</span></div></td>
        </tr>
